Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.90,0:02:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第十話 再生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.50,0:02:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真早啊，Eclair
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.10,0:03:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,E…Eclair
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.30,0:03:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麽回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.50,0:03:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,平時總是說著“遲到啦”沖進來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.40,0:03:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天要是沒有下雨就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.80,0:03:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了，是熬夜了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.70,0:03:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不要來杯咖啡，濃些的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.70,0:03:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思，給我來杯茶吧，今天休息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.00,0:03:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麽來杯菊花茶吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.30,0:03:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有鎮靜作用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.60,0:03:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(鎮靜劑)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.90,0:03:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓您久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.30,0:03:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.80,0:03:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等，茶和鎮靜劑可不能一起吃啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.70,0:03:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，卡普利斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.90,0:04:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨，早上好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.40,0:04:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.10,0:04:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.90,0:05:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又裝太多了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.90,0:05:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慣用的藉口可說不過去了喲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.40,0:05:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要不浪費後備的份就沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.70,0:05:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了，系統停止了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.10,0:05:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放這裏了喲，Eclipse
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.50,0:05:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eclipse？局長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.20,0:05:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從在這裏第一次見到你們的肮髒的臉開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.80,0:05:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到現在已經有半年，小夥子們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.30,0:05:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然聽說也有夾著尾巴逃跑的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.40,0:05:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但在這裏的你們，看來相當喜歡這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.20,0:06:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，大家也都十分明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.10,0:06:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們國家行星聯邦和行星共和國聯合之間\N進入了戰爭狀態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.30,0:06:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一眨眼已經三個月了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.60,0:06:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.00,0:06:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能一直養著你們這些小子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.00,0:06:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結束了，諸君從現在開始，赴任于各自的崗位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.30,0:06:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.40,0:06:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向諸君傳達我最後的命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.90,0:06:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“別死”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.60,0:06:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,解散
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.20,0:06:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放我出去！放我出去！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.10,0:06:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放這些人出去的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.10,0:06:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又會有數億人死去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.20,0:07:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爲什麽？爲什麽？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.80,0:07:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到了命令的時間了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.30,0:07:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發射不了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.60,0:07:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不想發射，這是我自己的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.20,0:07:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舉起手來，雙手握拳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.50,0:07:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然沒用…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.40,0:07:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麽會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.90,0:07:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在離開Aineias之前就已經設置好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.30,0:07:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aineias？這是GOTT的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.80,0:07:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.80,0:07:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.90,0:07:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肚子餓了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.60,0:08:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,摸這裏我也不會給你喂奶哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.20,0:08:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要太過分了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.60,0:08:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.90,0:08:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做惡夢了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.30,0:08:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.40,0:08:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，卡普利斯，是我不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.00,0:08:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麽？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.50,0:08:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,攢到現在的賬單
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.50,0:08:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麽？就是說再也不來了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.10,0:09:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eclair大傻瓜，再也不要來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.50,0:09:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.40,0:09:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(鎮靜劑)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.20,0:09:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這只是適合普通人吃的藥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.90,0:09:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有什麽意義吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.50,0:09:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麽說來，上次…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.80,0:09:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這頭紅發，這種動作，Eclair
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.00,0:09:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前任者的事情我一點都不知道啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.40,0:10:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前任者，是普裏霍爾德
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.20,0:10:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我以前，用化名“Eclair”的人們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.60,0:10:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前任者，是普裏霍爾德
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.20,0:10:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是的，我才不是什麽前任者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.60,0:10:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.40,0:10:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種事情我知道，你就是我自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.70,0:10:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.20,0:10:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無動于衷的殺掉別人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.90,0:10:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有自己死了一次又一次却能延續生命活下來的女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.10,0:10:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“前任者”，這樣假扮他人可不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.70,0:10:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的手，已經沾滿了鮮血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.10,0:11:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，是Eclair
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.90,0:11:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,局長，Eclair來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.50,0:11:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.80,0:11:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,局長，那個，Eclair她…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.90,0:11:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝，Mercredi
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.00,0:11:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告辭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.90,0:12:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.30,0:12:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，是你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.20,0:12:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是奧美加，正在進行中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.40,0:12:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在的等級是E級
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.70,0:12:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,獲得的數據現在是預定的8成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.30,0:12:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坐標已經傳送完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.60,0:12:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,E4的樣本也拿到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.90,0:12:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對手也是ES成員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.90,0:12:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不可能是Pelias政府的人
