Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.10,0:14:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很期待吧，Eclair小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.00,0:14:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.50,0:14:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那幫傢伙暴跳如雷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.00,0:14:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還扮女裝，挑逗得過火了點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.60,0:14:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看到他們的表情了嗎？
