Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.00,0:14:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麽了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.00,0:14:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道，速度…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.70,0:14:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陷進了力場中，是他們的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.50,0:15:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,纏著不放的男人會被討厭的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.90,0:15:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,TP
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.80,0:15:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡，慣性驅動怎麽回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.20,0:15:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先被相位干涉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.20,0:15:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.10,0:15:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然能理解你們的心情
